    public class SubresultIndexer<I,R extends AbstractDSVisSubresult<I>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMatrixDataSource<I,R>, java.lang.Iterable<R>
    Holds all generated subresults/images and provides some basic (matrix-like) interface for them. The matrix may not be complete (some positions may be blank).
